// These commands compile Executive/11// The following definitions files are required for one// or more of the compilations below://        ComStruct.bcpl        - Part of Executive.dm//        AltoDefs.d            - OS//        AltoFileSys.d//        BcplFiles.d//        Disks.d//        Disp.d//        Streams.d//        SysDefs.d//        Time.d                - Time.dmbcpl/F NewCommand.bcplbcpl/F ExecInput.bcplbcpl/F DKS.bcplbcpl/F Drtns2.bcplbcpl/F QMaint.bcplbcpl/F Sort.bcplasm/l LocalTab.asmbcpl/F ExecInit.bcplbcpl/F OnceOnly.bcplbcpl/F Type.bcplbcpl/F Partition.bcplbcpl/F SetTime.bcplbcpl/F QFD.bcplbcpl/F Rename.bcplbcpl/F DumpLoad.bcplbcpl/F SplitFileName.bcpl// In addition to the files above, several other .BR files are// required which are standard packages://        EtherBoot.br//        Format.br//        GP.br//        OverlaysInit.br      - Overlay.dm//        Overlays.br//        ReadUserCmItem.br//        RenameFile.br//        TimeConvA.br         - Time.dm package//        TimeConvB.br//        TimeIO.br